name: GA Views evaluation
description: Google Analytics properties contain views of the data. The views' information needs to be evaluated to ensure that the tracking is set appropriately.

constants.name: expectedProfileTypes
constants.description: Set of main view types that are expected to be present

blocks.description: Prepares data and checks presence of expected profile types
blocks.passMessage: All expected profile types (${expectedProfileTypesJoined}) are present.
blocks.failMessage: Some of the expected types are missing: ${missingProfileTypesJoined}

blocks.description: Checks if bot filtering is enabled
blocks.passMessage: Bot filtering is enabled on all views.
blocks.failMessage: Bot filtering not enabled at least on one of the views.

blocks.description: Checks if there is any view with website that has no protocol
blocks.passMessage: All views have websites with protocol defined.
blocks.failMessage: For at least one of the views the website URLs has no protocol.
